          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Because a VPN encrypts your data and routes it through an external server, you may experience a slight drop in speed. Top-tier providers optimize their networks so the reduction is often unnoticeable, especially with fast protocols like WireGuard."
